Green v. Smith. The evidence warranted the verdict, and there was no error in deny, ing a new trial. April 16, 1894.

Argued at the last term.

Judgment affirmed.

*702Levy and claim. Before Judge McWhorter. Early superior court. April term, 1893. R. H. Sheffield, by Harrison & Peeples, for plaintiff in error. R. H. Powell & Son. contra.
